    "ocr_text": "56
XXXXXXXXXXXXX Ouray Bldg.,
X.
Feb. 13, 1903.
Mr. Everett W. McGinnis, Secretary,
Central Labor Union,
2037 Ruckle St., Indianapolis, Ind.
Dear Sir and Brother:
Your favor of the 7th instant received and contents noted.
I have also noted your enclosures marked exhibits A, B, and C, and
I am free to express the opinion that in my judgment the Central
Labor Union should admit the Sawmiths' local #1 upon the basis
proposed by that organization.
With best wishes, I am,
Fraternally yours,



President,
American Federation of Labor.",
